Item 8.01. Other Events.
Shift4 Payments, Inc. (the “Company”) has been advised by the Financial Industry Regulatory Authority (“FINRA”) that, in accordance with FINRA
Rule 6440, trading of the Company's Class A Common Stock, $0.0001 par value per share (the “Common Stock”) on the New York Stock Exchange (the
“NYSE”), will be temporarily suspended at 7:30 a.m. (New York City time) on June 4, 2020, prior to the opening of trading on the NYSE. Trading in the
Common Stock is expected to resume on the NYSE at or around 9:30 a.m. (New York City time).
